https://zapier.com/
Sign in to ZAPIER via your google account.
On the zapier dashboard, select "Agents" from the left navigation panel to create a new agent. 
To use Googlesheets as Tools - Add tools > Search Google sheet 
Configure the Googlesheet tool added. Provide credentials to google drive and select the file with the Ecommerce Checkout incident data.
Select a trigger ( on demand / schedule)
Draft a system prompt to cover all the requirements
Webhook - If you do not have an API endpoint use the webhook.site for generating test URLs and view the Webhook JSON Payload being posted to the same.
If you want to avoid the webhook step - Use a Google Doc ( add as tool ) and configure the append to document method and test agents capability to generate JSON Payloads as intructed.
